{"tid":1191733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毀屍滅跡！支那毛匪廟剛被外媒曝光 當局忙派百人連夜剷平","createTime":"2019-06-08T05:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T06:16:11.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"16471f3484c887ce6364097d74a66fc2a5702c34","tid":1191733,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpecEScv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpecEScv.jpg&h=cfc3a727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國近期擴大迫害宗教，廣拆境內各宗教場所，河南省一座詭異廟宇將已故中共領導人毛澤東供為主神，不僅沒被打壓，還被當局視為紅色愛國主義教育基地而香火鼎盛。不過就在消息被外媒曝光後，當局疑為「毀屍滅跡」，隔天竟直接出動上百人，一夕之間將該廟剷平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6f2Hic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6f2Hic.jpg&h=4a020336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌5月11日曾刊文披露此亂象，稱這座「毛主席佛祖殿」位於河南省汝州市寄料鎮張坡村西約2公里處的青龍山上，進入大院可見一座大型露天毛澤東雕像，雕像底座刻有將毛澤東神化的詩句，「毛主就是新玉皇，統天統地統人間」。分析指出，這座廟疑因此規避政府迫害，甚至還有大批中共官員前來膜拜毛澤東。然而消息才剛曝光，隔天（5月12日）當地政府便動員上百名軍警，出動2台挖掘機，連夜把「毛主席佛祖殿」內所有房屋拆毀。據悉，除了大院中6公尺<br />\n高的毛澤東雕像被用塑膠布套上外，其餘雕像全被拆毀，現場人員更以鐵皮與土堆將大門封死，再派駐兩人看守廢墟，以防拆廟的消息再次外流。<br />\n <br />\n《寒冬》引述知情人士的說法指出，這次強拆命令是由河南省政府直接下達，為避免消息曝光，行動當晚寺廟方圓3公里內的地區全部戒嚴，參與拆廟行動的人員手機全被沒收，足見行事之慎重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FUKMSJD4Of8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFUKMSJD4Of8&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8zYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=35ed44ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FUKMSJD4Of8</a>"},{"pid":"6655fea00204834e3191dde7c77ec01675b28e7c","tid":1191733,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a089b532321e1c78178c7ba2197f0131c11963","tid":1191733,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"香港快d起維尼廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee864754d015e62f544e304a473dc4a947dff9d","tid":1191733,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SToAUVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSToAUVJ.png&h=115291e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vyu4OfK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyu4OfK.png&h=daeefe43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77edd7827bb8b75341df12a00e57e5295a76cd8f","tid":1191733,"uid":144012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"毛神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0225ed1775ed2d8d8b38a2b1a497b3e5ebe10b","tid":1191733,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:00:44.000Z","msg":"「宇宙天尊佛祖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6305c6fea5232b40e533ee3175afc5714e83e977","tid":1191733,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"毛賊神經病！"}]}